Package: vlfeat
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Computer vision command-line tools
 This package provides command-line tools built against
 libvlfeat. Libvlfeat is an Open Source 
 computer vision library specialized in features extraction
 and matching. It includes a free SIFT implementation. But 
 PLEASE NOTE that SIFT algorithm is patented and must not
 be used for commercial purpose.
 .
 Library packages (libvlfeat package and -dev package)
 will come soon.
